# - Hypervisor
# - Guest operating systems

# 5. Hypervisor
# Software used to create and manage virtual machines.

# Types:
# a) Type 1 Hypervisor
#    Runs directly on hardware.

# b) Type 2 Hypervisor
#    Runs on operating system.

# 6. Virtual Clustering
# Group of virtual machines working together.

# 7. Applications of Virtualization
# - Cloud computing
